{"tid":2056894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法庭要求律政司就公開催淚彈成份一案提交誓章","createTime":"2020-06-09T04:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T04:21:37.000Z","uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc55c0e0b391011188cafddf06211b16f5d36ce","tid":2056894,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"立法會議員許智峯早前入稟高等法院，要求警方公開催淚彈成份的案件，今日召開聆訊。法庭指示律政司需要在35日內，提交警方的法律觀點。許智峯對審訊表示樂觀，希望可以為受催淚煙影響的人，提出民事索償時爭取理據，長遠希望禁止警方使用催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1304170&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1304170%26csid%3D261_341&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=0d3f8edb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1304170&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}